headline: JKHY Gears Up to Report Q2 Earnings: What's in the Cards?
summary: Jack Henry & Associates gears up to report Q2 FY26 earnings on Feb. 3, with sales seen up 6.2% and EPS up 5.2%, as cloud, payments and services momentum builds.

headline: How A New Analyst Target Is Reframing The Story For Jack Henry & Associates (JKHY)
summary: Jack Henry & Associates is back in focus after analysts updated their price target, signaling a reassessment of what the stock could be worth based on the latest information and expectations. With no prior target to compare against, this new level effectively sets a fresh reference point for how the market may frame the story around the company.
